History and Heritage
The University of Debrecen  traces its roots back to the early 20th century when it was founded as a modest teacher training college. Over the years, it has evolved and expanded, embracing new disciplines and emerging as a comprehensive university with a global reputation for excellence in education and research. Today, the university proudly carries forward its rich heritage while embracing innovation and modernity in all aspects of its academic endeavors.

Academic Programs
The University of Debrecen  offers a diverse array of undergraduate, graduate, and doctoral programs across various fields of study. These include:

Medicine
Dentistry
